### **4. 23_LivePlotDash**  
**Description:**  
A lightweight tool to plot incoming numerical values as a real-time, dynamic line graph.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LivePlotDash - Realtime Data Visualization Tool

LivePlotDash allows you to chart sensor streams, simulations, or performance metrics as they happen.

## Features
- Smooth line updates  
- Adjustable interval  
- Matplotlib backend  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/23_LivePlotDash.git
cd 23_LivePlotDash
python visualize.py
